# Board Meetings

SPI holds its board meetings publicly on IRC using the #spi channel on
irc.spi-inc.org (part of the OFTC network). The by-laws state that this must
happen at least quarterly, but we aim for a monthly meeting at 20:00 UTC on
the third Wednesday of the month.

